class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ukk1665702596834.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ukk1665702596834.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ukk1665702596834.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ukk1665702596834\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__reset_235604\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__topic_d76277e1_d76278e1_d76279e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__p_d76280e1_d76281e1_d76282e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reset</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__section_w2053ab1b7b5_w2054ab1b7_w2055ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__p_d76283e1_d76284e1_d76285e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">reset $procerror</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__topic_d50117e1_d50118e1_d50119e1_d50120e1_d50121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d399656e80\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__d6481e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__d6481e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__d6481e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__d6481e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ukk1665702596834__d6481e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ukk1665702596834__d6481e20__entry__2\">Literal </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ukk1665702596834__d6481e20__entry__3\"> ProcScript function</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__topic_d50122e1_d50123e1_d50124e1_d50125e1_d50126e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d399656e134\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__table_d7223e1_d7224e1_d7225e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__table_d7223e1_d7224e1_d7225e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__table_d7223e1_d7224e1_d7225e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ukk1665702596834__table_d7223e1_d7224e1_d7225e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ukk1665702596834__table_d7223e1_d7224e1_d7225e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reset</span> cannot be used with\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ukk1665702596834__table_d7223e1_d7224e1_d7225e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ukk1665702596834__table_d7223e1_d7224e1_d7225e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var> was successfully reset.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__topic_d50127e1_d50128e1_d50129e1_d50130e1_d50131e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d399656e202\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__d6482e20\">Allowed in all component types except self-contained Report and Services.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__topic_d50132e1_d50133e1_d50134e1_d50135e1_d50136e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d399656e211\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__p_d76301e1_d76302e1_d76303e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reset</span> statement resets the value of the ProcScript function <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptFunction</var> to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FALSE</span> (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">0</span>). It can be used only with functions for which this feature is documented.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__section_imn_v3j_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d399656e232\">Example: Resetting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmod</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example sets the CITY field in a form, then resets the\n            component instance modification indicator, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmod</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ukk1665702596834__pre_bpv_v3j_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n city = \"New Orleans\" ; this sets $formmod to 1\n reset $formmod\n edit NAME\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eww1719683180873.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>set</a><p>Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532720\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532720\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "reset Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0 . reset ProcScriptFunction Example: reset $procerror Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description ProcScriptFunction Literal ProcScript function Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Meaning <0 reset cannot be used with ProcScriptFunction . 0 ProcScriptFunction was successfully reset. Use Allowed in all component types except self-contained Report and Services. Description The reset statement resets the value of the ProcScript function ProcScriptFunction to FALSE ( 0 ). It can be used only with functions for which this feature is documented. Example: Resetting $formmod The following example sets the CITY field in a form, then resets the component instance modification indicator, $formmod : operation exec city = \"New Orleans\" ; this sets $formmod to 1 reset $formmod edit NAME end Copy Related Links set Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}